item.title: I cant see anyone on server? help
item.dc:creator: @HelpMePlz249 HelpMePlz249
item.description:
@HelpMePlz249 wrote:

[quote=“IcyPimp, post:8, topic:18621”][quote author=HelpMePlz249 link=topic=28173.msg323759#msg323759 date=1161067120]
yes its 127.0.0.1 what am I suppose to do?
[/quote]

You find someone else’s I.P.

127.0.0.1 is, as escape said, your local host. It connects you to your own I.P. So, for example, if you and your friend are trying to meet eachother, you can’t say “pomfg les go get full dragun n 127.0.0.1”, because he would be connecting to his I.P. and you would be connecting to yours. You need either Hamachi or a No-IP to have someone else connect to you.[/quote]

So im suppose to get someone elses IP and stick it in there? How am I suppose to get it?
